OL,3,CCalls for more awareness of Alopecia
OL,4,Cin Guernsey
OL,6,FEmma Johns, who herself has alopecia,
OL,7,Fhas set up Guernsey's first Alopecia
OL,8,Fnetwork to encourage more people to
OL,9,Ftalk about it.
OL,11,FAlopecia is an autoimmune disease that
OL,12,Faffects one in 1000 people - the body
OL,13,Fattacks hair follicles which can cause
OL,14,Fhair loss.
OL,16,FEmma was just 14 years old when she
OL,17,Fnoticed large clumps of hair falling
OL,18,Fout.
