OL,3,CCalls for more awareness of Alopecia
OL,4,Cin Guernsey
OL,6,FEmma opened the support group in the
OL,7,Fhope of providing a safe space for
OL,8,Fisladers in Guernsey to share
OL,9,Fexperiences, offer advice, and build
OL,10,Fconnections.
OL,12,FEncouraged by Alopecia UK and Jersey's
OL,13,Fexperience with this kind of group,
OL,14,FEmma has now established a support
OL,15,Fnetwork for Guernsey with their first
OL,16,Fmeeting in two week's time.
