OL,3,CCalls for more awareness of Alopecia
OL,4,Cin Guernsey
OL,6,FSue Schilling from Alopecia UK said:
OL,7,F"The impacts for many people are
OL,8,Fpsychological. People report a loss of
OL,9,Fself esteem, self-esteem. We know that
OL,10,Fthere is an increase in depression and
OL,11,Fanxiety for people with alopecia and
OL,12,Fpeople report this loss of identity.
OL,13,FI'm looking in the mirror and I don't
OL,14,Fknow who's looking back at me anymore."
OL,16,FElena McGowan told ITV News earlier in
OL,17,Fthe year how she felt ignored and let
OL,18,Fdown by her medical care when she lost
OL,19,Fher hair in just 6 weeks.
