OL,3,CCalls for more awareness of Alopecia
OL,4,Cin Guernsey
OL,6,FShe set up Jersey's first support
OL,7,Fgroup for people with Alopecia 7 years
OL,8,Fago and says things have now improved.
OL,10,FShe said: "I am told by members of my
OL,11,Fgroup who access treatment to access
OL,12,Fthe hospital that there is now a
OL,13,Freally positive approach to treatment,
OL,14,Fwhich is amazing, people are being
OL,15,Ftreated and it's just really positive
OL,16,Fand their experiences at the hospital,
OL,17,Fif they choose to go."
